"Change Set:		7935PreferenceBrowser-MAD.38PreferenceBrowser-MAD.38:Selection highlighting in lists is now consistent with that in menus. I've made direct reference to Preferences menuSelectionColor - not sure if this will be seen as reasonable?You should really tone down the highlight colour after loading these changes:Preferences setParameter: #menuSelectionColor to: (Color r: 0.4 g: 0.5 b: 0.7)"!!PBPreferenceButtonMorph methodsFor: 'highlighting' stamp: 'MAD 10/6/2009 19:35'!highlightOn		self color: (Color gray alpha: 0.1).		self addExtraControls.! !